      "from": "auto-orchestrator",
      "to": "my-docs",
      "trigger": "User wants ANYTHING about their documents, cloud storage, or indexed corpora: connecting Dropbox or Google Drive, listing cloud folders/files, ingesting / indexing folders, corpus management, searching document content, analyzing contracts/handbooks/specs, multi-hop reasoning over docs, checking sync or indexing status. ANY question that mentions Dropbox, Google Drive, Drive, corpus, indexing, documents, contracts, handbooks, or document-files (not phone contacts) \u2014 hand off here.",
