      "_auto_generated": true
    },
    {
      "id": "auto-orch-to-mycoach",
      "from": "auto-orchestrator",
      "to": "mycoach",
      "trigger": "HIGHEST PRIORITY for ANY coaching/nutrition/fitness/activity/habit request. MyCoach is the user's personal AI coach. Hand off here for: (1) Food/meal/drink/plate/dish PHOTOS \u2014 anything edible. (2) Logging meals: 'I had X', 'log my breakfast/lunch/dinner/snack', 'I just ate Y'. (3) Calorie/macro/water tracking, hydration, daily/weekly diet summaries, nutrition goals. (4) Meal-planning and diet-advice requests: 'what should I eat today', 'plan my meals', 'suggest a healthy lunch'. (5) ANY phrase referring to a 'coach/nutritionist/dietitian/nutrition specialist/nutrition advisor/personal coach/fitness coach/trainer' \u2014 these refer to the MYCOACH SKILL (an AI role), NOT to a human contact. NEVER search contacts for a 'coach' or 'nutritionist'; just hand off here. (6) Activity/fitness questions: steps, workouts, walking, exercise, 'should I work out'. (7) Wellbeing / habit questions: energy levels, sleep, mood, 'how am I doing'. (8) Anything containing: nutrition, diet, calories, macros, protein, carbs, fat, hydration, meal, breakfast, lunch, dinner, snack, eat, ate, eating, coach, coaching, workout, exercise, steps, fitness, walk, run, activity.",
